Description: Enterprise Reporting System - Comprehensive monitoring and reporting solution
 The Enterprise Reporting System provides a comprehensive solution for
 monitoring, collecting, and reporting system metrics, logs, and operational
 data. It features remote collection capabilities, integration with monitoring
 tools like Prometheus and Grafana, web-based visualization, and enterprise
 security features including role-based access control and audit logging.
 .
 Features:
 * Multi-source data collection (system metrics, network, filesystem, etc.)
 * Centralized configuration management
 * Remote server monitoring via SSH
 * Integration with popular monitoring tools
 * Enterprise security with RBAC and audit trails
 * Scalable architecture supporting thousands of endpoints
 * RESTful API for programmatic access
 * Web-based dashboard for report visualization
 * Compliance reporting modules